{"tid":1831204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Refund]關於要求學校就要斬上學期退回學費一事","createTime":"2020-01-20T08:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T13:27:26.000Z","uid":14503,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b8eca1f61681170e3d47cd1a96ec2f537e641b11","tid":1831204,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:32:10.000Z","msg":"原post:<br />\n大學班高層傾緊refund上學期部分學費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道有學院已經有代表約左同學校傾，所以學校急急腳係傾之前收左sem 2學費先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋睇個勢係你唔同佢傾佢就唔理你，可能淨係entertain同佢傾個班人，同埋會組織學生代表去傾既好多都係中國學生，反而本地學生who fucking care, 無人組織去同學校傾，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SU又唔做野</span></span></strong>CLS<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家真係要一人一信要求學校回水，另外各自搵代表同學校傾，另外SU 呢？ 出黎交代下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"71192569e46545770110b2b865e09588c3ac55c8","tid":1831204,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6788e9097053098b246dacd64903cc158a995b5d","tid":1831204,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:35:22.000Z","msg":"壓榨學生最叻 大專教育根本係一門生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d5b8b4722ada73f22b8212b1cb778744bbc34d","tid":1831204,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"一係全世界拖學費拖到deadline 交？如果有人傾都有少少bargaining power"},{"pid":"38837ca4c1d7249fd0f3c71b74ceca12ee